\subsection{Observations}

\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em]
  \item Training loss decreases \textbf{monotonically} from 1.24 to 0.21, indicating successful gradient-based optimisation.
  \item Validation accuracy \textbf{oscillates} between $\approx$79–83\%, suggesting moderate overfitting on the small dataset.
  \item The best validation accuracy of \textbf{83.33\%} is achieved at Epoch 7, after which the model begins to slightly overfit.
  \item The gap between training convergence and validation plateau can be addressed by stronger regularisation or a larger dataset.
\end{itemize}

